# ePassGen by Gr√©gory Saive (@eVias)
# Generate one or more passwords instantly.
# Thanks for reading me, enjoy

#--------------------------------
# Usage :

# eVias@[eviasdev:/home/user/evias/dev/cpp/ePassGen] : 
make build

# to generate 100 passwords of length 8 in a grid
# eVias@[eviasdev:/home/user/evias/dev/cpp/ePassGen] :
.bin/ePassGen

# to generate 7 passwords of length 8 in a grid
# eVias@[eviasdev:/home/user/evias/dev/cpp/ePassGen] :
.bin/ePassGen 7

# to generate 11 passwords of length 6 in a grid
# eVias@[eviasdev:/home/user/evias/dev/cpp/ePassGen] :
.bin/ePassGen 11 6
#--------------------------------



#--------------------------------
# Clean:

# to clean the junk (*.o) directory only
# eVias@[eviasdev:/home/user/evias/dev/cpp/ePassGen] :
make clean

# to clean the junk (*.o) AND the executable file
# eVias@[eviasdev:/home/user/evias/dev/cpp/ePassGen] :
make mrpropre
#--------------------------------


#--------------------------------
# Needs for compile

- libstdc++
- g++ make
#--------------------------------
